            <sparkle:version>2.0.30</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>2.0.30</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[<h2>Bug Fixes</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Improved onboarding interview flow with better wording and more accurate context generation</li>
  <li>Fixed an issue where meeting recordings could be lost if the app was quit or crashed during recording</li>
  <li>Fixed missing meeting recordings caused by a race condition</li>
  <li>Improved reliability of the dictation process so that individual failures no longer interrupt the entire workflow</li>
  <li>General improvements to retry logic for more stable recording uploads</li>
</ul>
]]></description>
